data.description: Welcome Home!! Just the single story 4 bedroom family home you've been looking for! You've got to see this corner home on oversized lot. This lovely floor plan has four comfortable bedrooms, and 2 full bathrooms. You will find that this well maintained home features dine-in kitchen, granite counter tops with high bar seating, separate garden tub and shower in the primary bath, high ceilings, ceiling fans, and much more. Truly a lovely place to call home, come and see for yourself. Pack your things and come on Home!!
